{"tid":1957211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抨醫院防疫不力 美華裔醫生被炒","createTime":"2020-04-03T17:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T17:56:43.000Z","uid":160319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"98b640e5a4e6fd01b1147ae507a56abeca27229d","tid":1957211,"uid":160319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"（星島日報報道）美國華盛頓州一名華裔急症室醫生，在社交網站貼文批評醫院新冠肺炎防疫措施不足後遭解僱。林明（Ming Lin，音譯）在貝靈厄姆的和平健康聖約瑟醫療中心工作已十七年，上月二十七日，他在facebook證實被外判商僱主「健康團隊」（Teamhealth）辭退。過去數周，林明在facebook批評醫院沒有足夠預防措施應對新冠肺炎，包括沒有篩檢所有病人，讓沒有戴口罩的病人留在人多擠逼的候診室，護士也沒有足夠保護裝備，敦促院方保障醫護人員。林明稱首次發聲後，即有主管威脅會終止其職務，並要求他撤回帖文，但他拒絕。該醫療中心目前有數名職員染疫，但院方強調並非因工感染。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4185223/2020-04-03/post-%e6%8a%a8%e9%86%ab%e9%99%a2%e9%98%b2%e7%96%ab%e4%b8%8d%e5%8a%9b-%e7%be%8e%e8%8f%af%e8%a3%94%e9%86%ab%e7%94%9f%e8%a2%ab%e7%82%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4185223%2F2020-04-03%2Fpost-%25e6%258a%25a8%25e9%2586%25ab%25e9%2599%25a2%25e9%2598%25b2%25e7%2596%25ab%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%258a%259b-%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%258f%25af%25e8%25a3%2594%25e9%2586%25ab%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e7%2582%2592%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=713a68e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/4185223/2020-04-03/post-%e6%8a%a8%e9%86%ab%e9%99%a2%e9%98%b2%e7%96%ab%e4%b8%8d%e5%8a%9b-%e7%be%8e%e8%8f%af%e8%a3%94%e9%86%ab%e7%94%9f%e8%a2%ab%e7%82%92/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實每個地方每個政權都係咁上下操作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561cf8cfe6d93f67ae97c7db85dfb1dd72f7f57b","tid":1957211,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"醫生都有外判<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668b75e584f91d5ad01914509a7d733862f816e4","tid":1957211,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":